'''Anx''' was the language of the [[Anx/Legends|Anx]] of [[Gravlex Med/Legends|Gravlex Med]], referring either to the spoken or written form. The Anx spoken language was comprised of words spoken in low-frequency tones produced by the [[Sinuses|sinus cavities]] found in an Anx's large headcrest. These tones could be heard across great distances.<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

